#Authorization: Bearer your-access-token-here

### 모든 사용자 목록 (페이징 포함)
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/users/users/paged?page=1&size=10&order=asc
Content-Type: application/json

### 특정 사용자 조회
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/users/14
Content-Type: application/json

### 사용자 생성
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "1newuser",
  "email": "1newuser@example.com",
  "full_name": "1New User",
  "password": "securepassword"
}

### 사용자 비밀번호 변경
PATCH http://localhost:8000/v1/users/14/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "111111"
}

### 사용자 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8000/v1/users/30
Content-Type: application/json
